Package: prodlim
Title: Product-Limit Estimation for Censored Event History Analysis
Version: 2018.04.18
Author: Thomas A. Gerds
Description: Fast and user friendly implementation of nonparametric
    estimators for censored event history (survival) analysis.
    Kaplan-Meier and Aalen-Johansen method.
